{"word":"H3563 - כֹּוס - kôwç - koce - Cup","slug":"H3563","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כֹּוס</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kôwç"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>koce"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cup"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05E1; - ko&#x0302;s</b> - <i>koce</i><p/>From an unused root meaning to <i>hold</i> together; a <i>cup</i> (as a container), often figuratively a <i>lot</i> (as if a potion); also some unclean bird, probably an <i>owl</i> (perhaps from the cup like cavity of its eye): - cup, (small) owl. Compare <a href=\"#/H3599\">H3599</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3199\">H3199</a>, <a href=\"#/H3200\">H3200</a>, <a href=\"#/H3204\">H3204</a>, <a href=\"#/H3559\">H3559</a>, <a href=\"#/H3560\">H3560</a>, <a href=\"#/H3561\">H3561</a>, <a href=\"#/H3562\">H3562</a>, <a href=\"#/H3651\">H3651</a>, <a href=\"#/H4349\">H4349</a>, <a href=\"#/H4350\">H4350</a>, <a href=\"#/H4369\">H4369</a>, <a href=\"#/H5225\">H5225</a>, <a href=\"#/H8498\">H8498</a>, <a href=\"#/H8499\">H8499</a>"}]}